<p><code>hazelcast.partition.group.rack</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>hazelcast.partition.group.host</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>hazelcast.hotrestart.free.native.memory.percentage</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
