<p>We would like to thank the contributors from our open source
community who worked on this release:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/AndrewKolpakov">Andrew Kolpakov</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
