<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>RC1 Fixes</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The following are the fixed issues for 3.2-RC1 (Release Candidate 1)
release.</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><em>TransactionalMap</em> does not support <code>put(K,V,long,TimeUnit)</code>.
